These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, juice, mirinda
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, bird, hamster, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | cola | sprite | mirinda | juice |
| Pet        | hedgehog | bird   | guinea-pig | hamster    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts, animation, action
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, polish, italian, australian
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
2. the canadian is on the left of the italian##1
3. the italian is in an odd position##4
4. the canadian is the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the polish is on the right of the italian##1
6. the canadian is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | adventure  | martial-arts  | action |
| Nationality   | australian    | canadian | italian | polish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, raspberry, artichoke, lime
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, thriller, horror, martial-arts
1. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
2. the person eating artichoke is in an even position##4
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | lime | artichoke | raspberry    | peas      |
| Movie-Genre   | horror        | martial-arts     | zombie | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, camping, traveling, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, funk, rock, trance
1. the person who's hobby is camping is between the fan of soul and the fan of trance##2
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the fan of rock is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of trance##1
5. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | chess | camping | traveling |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | soul   | funk    | trance  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, house, soul, dubstep
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, thai, malaysian, japanese
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the japanese##1
2. the thai is the fan of dubstep##1
3. the malaysian is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
4. the fan of house is on the far left##1
5. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | house  | electronic    | soul   | dubstep       |
| Nationality   | canadian | japanese | malaysian | thai |

