4. the russian is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the pakistani is on the left or right of the russian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance      | comedy | crime | fantasy |
| Nationality   | nigerian | canadian     | russian  | pakistani  |

