.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, lawyer, analyst, nurse
4 different pets are kept: hamster, ferret, goldfish, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
2. the nurse is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the nurse##3
4. the nurse is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the writer is between the nurse and the lawyer##2
6. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the ferret is between the writer and the owner of the goldfish##2
8. the writer is on the left or right of the lawyer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | lawyer | writer      | nurse | analyst |
| Pet   | hamster  | chinchilla | ferret    | goldfish            |

