.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, artichoke, papaya, cranberry
4 different pets are kept: bird, lizard, guinea-pig, horse
1. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
2. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
3. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the lizard and the person eating papaya##2
4. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating papaya is the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | cranberry | artichoke   | lemon | papaya |
| Pet    | horse     | lizard | bird     | guinea-pig  |

