.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, 7up, mirinda
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, reggae, salsa, r&b
1. the person drinking milk is the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the fan of r&b is between the fan of ambient and the person drinking 7up##2
4. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | 7up   | milk | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | reggae | r&b        | ambient    |

