.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up, hot-chocolate, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, skateboarding, handball, swimming
1. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda   | lemonade   | 7up      | hot-chocolate      |
| Sport      | skateboarding | handball | swimming | surfing |

