3. the person eating cucumber is in an even position##4
4. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the fan of techno and the fan of trance##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | spinach | cucumber  | pumpkin  | pear |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | trance | salsa | techno   |

