.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, reading, rock-climbing, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, tennis, rowing, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's hobby is reading##2
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | sudoku | reading         | traveling   | rock-climbing |
| Sport   | rowing    | tennis | surfing | snowboarding   |

