.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, cooking, dancing, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, volleyball, snowboarding, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | cooking | sudoku | dancing    | filmmaking |
| Sport   | biathlon   | snowboarding  | sailing | volleyball     |

