3. the canadian is the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the italian is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the canadian is between the russian and the italian##2
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
