.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, tea, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: radish, garlic, onion, papaya
1. the person eating garlic is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
5. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person eating onion is in an even position##4
7. the person eating radish is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | iced-tea    | tea       | hot-chocolate |
| Food       | garlic  | onion | papaya | radish  |

