.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, egyptian, spanish, italian
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, ship, roller, van
1. the brazilian is on the left of the italian##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the spanish##1
5. the brazilian is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
6. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | egyptian | spanish | brazilian  | italian |
| Transport     | subway      | roller       | ship | van     |

