.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, dancer, writer, project-manager
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, airplane, skateboard
1. the dancer is in an even position##4
2. the dancer is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the photographer and the person driving the scooter##2
4. the dancer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the project-manager##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | photographer | writer   | project-manager | dancer |
| Transport   | skateboard          | quad-bike | scooter         | airplane  |

 